data.description: Welcome to your dream lakeside retreat! This stunning 4-sided brick home offers the perfect blend of lakelife, country living, but shopping and convenience are only minutes away!  Nestled on a lake stocked with catfish, crappie, and bass, this property is a haven for fishing enthusiasts and nature lovers alike.  Main Residence: Immaculately Maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, Cozy fireplace in the spacious living room for cozy evenings, Well-appointed kitchen with modern appliances and ample storage, Serene master bedroom with ensuite bathroom, Panoramic views of the lake from the interior, but Step out and Enjoy the Enclosed Patio, and Expansive Backyard. It is comforting and a beautiful sight to appreciate...Easy lake access right in your backyard!  Additional Features: _Bonus 1-bedroom apartment with a private entrance _Separate bathroom for added convenience _Kitchenette for independent living or guest quarters _Ample parking space for residents and guests  Rent out the Apartment for additional income, or use it as Teen or In-Law Suite!!! Possibilities are Endless!!   Outdoors: -Your own private paradise for fishing and relaxation!  Minutes from Robins Air Force Base, Affordable Cost of Living, Medical Facilities and Hospital Nearby, Growing Area w/ Strong Economy, Family Friendly w/ Community Events, and Convenient to Major Highways and Nearby Attractions, Reputable Schools!!! Warner Robins Has Alot to Offer for New Residents!!
